spec.collapsedText: "The iPhone 13 mini is Apple's smaller product of iPhone 14 with a 5.4" screen size, it comes with a 120Hz ProMotion display for super smooth scrolling. The list of innovations includes a more capable triple camera setup, with a wide, ultra-wide and zoom cameras, as well as a LiDAR scanner.
